{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I thought I'd begin with a scene of war."},{"time":3000,"text":"There was little to warn of the danger ahead."},{"time":5000,"text":"The Iraqi insurgent had placed the IED,"},{"time":7000,"text":"an Improvised Explosive Device,"},{"time":10000,"text":"along the side of the road with great care."},{"time":12000,"text":"By 2006, there were more than 2,500"},{"time":16000,"text":"of these attacks every single month,"},{"time":19000,"text":"and they were the leading cause of"},{"time":21000,"text":"casualties among American soldiers"},{"time":23000,"text":"and Iraqi civilians."},{"time":25000,"text":"The team that was hunting for this IED"},{"time":27000,"text":"is called an EOD team—"},{"time":29000,"text":"Explosives Ordinance Disposal—and"},{"time":31000,"text":"they're the pointy end of the spear in the"},{"time":33000,"text":"American effort to suppress these roadside bombs."},{"time":36000,"text":"Each EOD team goes out on about"},{"time":38000,"text":"600 of these bomb calls every year,"},{"time":40000,"text":"defusing about two bombs a day."},{"time":43000,"text":"Perhaps the best sign of how valuable they"},{"time":45000,"text":"are to the war effort, is that"},{"time":47000,"text":"the Iraqi insurgents put a $50,000 bounty"},{"time":49000,"text":"on the head of a single EOD soldier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52000,"text":"Unfortunately, this particular call"},{"time":54000,"text":"would not end well."},{"time":56000,"text":"By the time the soldier advanced close"},{"time":58000,"text":"enough to see the telltale wires"},{"time":60000,"text":"of the bomb, it exploded in a wave of flame."},{"time":63000,"text":"Now, depending how close you are"},{"time":65000,"text":"and how much explosive has been packed"},{"time":67000,"text":"into that bomb, it can cause death"},{"time":69000,"text":"or injury. You have to be as far as"},{"time":71000,"text":"50 yards away to escape that."},{"time":73000,"text":"The blast is so strong it can even break"},{"time":75000,"text":"your limbs, even if you're not hit."},{"time":77000,"text":"That soldier had been on top of the bomb."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"And so when the rest of the team advanced"},{"time":82000,"text":"they found little left. And that night the unit's"},{"time":84000,"text":"commander did a sad duty, and he wrote"},{"time":86000,"text":"a condolence letter back to the United"},{"time":88000,"text":"States, and he talked about how hard the"},{"time":90000,"text":"loss had been on his unit, about the fact"},{"time":92000,"text":"that they had lost their bravest soldier,"},{"time":94000,"text":"a soldier who had saved their lives"},{"time":96000,"text":"many a time."},{"time":98000,"text":"And he apologized"},{"time":100000,"text":"for not being able to bring them home."},{"time":102000,"text":"But then he talked up the silver lining"},{"time":104000,"text":"that he took away from the loss."},{"time":106000,"text":"\"At least,\" as he wrote, \"when a robot dies,"},{"time":108000,"text":"you don't have to write a letter"},{"time":110000,"text":"to its mother.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":112000,"text":"That scene sounds like science fiction,"},{"time":114000,"text":"but is battlefield reality already."},{"time":116000,"text":"The soldier in that case"},{"time":119000,"text":"was a 42-pound robot called a PackBot."},{"time":122000,"text":"The chief's letter went, not to some"},{"time":125000,"text":"farmhouse in Iowa like you see"},{"time":127000,"text":"in the old war movies, but went to"},{"time":130000,"text":"the iRobot Company, which is"},{"time":132000,"text":"named after the Asimov novel"},{"time":135000,"text":"and the not-so-great Will Smith movie,"},{"time":137000,"text":"and... um... (Laughter)..."},{"time":139000,"text":"if you remember that"},{"time":141000,"text":"in that fictional world, robots started out"},{"time":143000,"text":"carrying out mundane chores, and then"},{"time":145000,"text":"they started taking on life-and-death decisions."},{"time":147000,"text":"That's a reality we face today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149000,"text":"What we're going to do is actually just"},{"time":151000,"text":"flash a series of photos behind me that"},{"time":153000,"text":"show you the reality of robots used in war"},{"time":156000,"text":"right now or already at the prototype stage."},{"time":158000,"text":"It's just to give you a taste."},{"time":161000,"text":"Another way of putting it is you're not"},{"time":163000,"text":"going to see anything that's powered"},{"time":165000,"text":"by Vulcan technology, or teenage"},{"time":167000,"text":"wizard hormones or anything like that."},{"time":169000,"text":"This is all real. So why don't we"},{"time":171000,"text":"go ahead and start those pictures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173000,"text":"Something big is going on in war today,"},{"time":175000,"text":"and maybe even the history of humanity"},{"time":177000,"text":"itself. The U.S. military went into Iraq with"},{"time":180000,"text":"a handful of drones in the air."},{"time":182000,"text":"We now have 5,300."},{"time":185000,"text":"We went in with zero unmanned ground"},{"time":187000,"text":"systems. We now have 12,000."},{"time":191000,"text":"And the tech term \"killer application\""},{"time":193000,"text":"takes on new meaning in this space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"And we need to remember that we're"},{"time":198000,"text":"talking about the Model T Fords,"},{"time":200000,"text":"the Wright Flyers, compared"},{"time":202000,"text":"to what's coming soon."},{"time":204000,"text":"That's where we're at right now."},{"time":206000,"text":"One of the people that I recently met with"},{"time":208000,"text":"was an Air Force three-star general, and he"},{"time":210000,"text":"said basically, where we're headed very"},{"time":212000,"text":"soon is tens of thousands of robots"},{"time":214000,"text":"operating in our conflicts, and these"},{"time":216000,"text":"numbers matter, because we're not just"},{"time":218000,"text":"talking about tens of thousands of today's"},{"time":220000,"text":"robots, but tens of thousands of these"},{"time":222000,"text":"prototypes and tomorrow's robots, because"},{"time":224000,"text":"of course, one of the things that's operating"},{"time":227000,"text":"in technology is Moore's Law,"},{"time":229000,"text":"that you can pack in more and more"},{"time":231000,"text":"computing power into those robots, and so"},{"time":233000,"text":"flash forward around 25 years,"},{"time":235000,"text":"if Moore's Law holds true,"},{"time":237000,"text":"those robots will be close to a billion times"},{"time":240000,"text":"more powerful in their computing than today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"And so what that means is the kind of"},{"time":245000,"text":"things that we used to only talk about at"},{"time":247000,"text":"science fiction conventions like Comic-Con"},{"time":249000,"text":"have to be talked about in the halls"},{"time":251000,"text":"of power and places like the Pentagon."},{"time":253000,"text":"A robots revolution is upon us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256000,"text":"Now, I need to be clear here."},{"time":258000,"text":"I'm not talking about a revolution where you"},{"time":260000,"text":"have to worry about the Governor of"},{"time":262000,"text":"California showing up at your door,"},{"time":264000,"text":"a la the Terminator. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":266000,"text":"When historians look at this period, they're"},{"time":268000,"text":"going to conclude that we're in a different"},{"time":270000,"text":"type of revolution: a revolution in war,"},{"time":272000,"text":"like the invention of the atomic bomb."},{"time":274000,"text":"But it may be even bigger than that,"},{"time":276000,"text":"because our unmanned systems don't just"}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"affect the \"how\" of war-fighting,"},{"time":280000,"text":"they affect the \"who\" of fighting"},{"time":282000,"text":"at its most fundamental level."},{"time":284000,"text":"That is, every previous revolution in war, be"},{"time":286000,"text":"it the machine gun, be it the atomic bomb,"},{"time":288000,"text":"was about a system that either shot faster,"},{"time":291000,"text":"went further, had a bigger boom."},{"time":294000,"text":"That's certainly the case with robotics, but"},{"time":297000,"text":"they also change the experience of the warrior"},{"time":300000,"text":"and even the very identity of the warrior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303000,"text":"Another way of putting this is that"},{"time":306000,"text":"mankind's 5,000-year-old monopoly"},{"time":308000,"text":"on the fighting of war is breaking down"},{"time":311000,"text":"in our very lifetime. I've spent"},{"time":313000,"text":"the last several years going around"},{"time":315000,"text":"meeting with all the players in this field,"},{"time":317000,"text":"from the robot scientists to the science"},{"time":319000,"text":"fiction authors who inspired them to the"},{"time":321000,"text":"19-year-old drone pilots who are fighting"},{"time":323000,"text":"from Nevada, to the four-star generals"},{"time":325000,"text":"who command them, to even the Iraqi"},{"time":327000,"text":"insurgents who they are targeting and what"},{"time":329000,"text":"they think about our systems, and"},{"time":331000,"text":"what I found interesting is not just"},{"time":333000,"text":"their stories, but how their experiences"},{"time":335000,"text":"point to these ripple effects that are going"},{"time":337000,"text":"outwards in our society, in our law"},{"time":339000,"text":"and our ethics, etc. And so what I'd like"},{"time":341000,"text":"to do with my remaining time is basically"},{"time":343000,"text":"flesh out a couple of these."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345000,"text":"So the first is that the future of war,"},{"time":347000,"text":"even a robotics one, is not going to be"},{"time":349000,"text":"purely an American one."},{"time":351000,"text":"The U.S. is currently ahead in military"},{"time":353000,"text":"robotics right now, but we know that in"},{"time":355000,"text":"technology there's no such thing as"},{"time":357000,"text":"a permanent first move or advantage."},{"time":360000,"text":"In a quick show of hands, how many"},{"time":362000,"text":"people in this room still use"},{"time":364000,"text":"Wang Computers? (Laughter)"},{"time":366000,"text":"It's the same thing in war. The British and"},{"time":368000,"text":"the French invented the tank."},{"time":371000,"text":"The Germans figured out how"},{"time":373000,"text":"to use it right, and so what we have to"},{"time":375000,"text":"think about for the U.S. is that we are"},{"time":377000,"text":"ahead right now, but you have"},{"time":379000,"text":"43 other countries out there"},{"time":381000,"text":"working on military robotics, and they"},{"time":383000,"text":"include all the interesting countries like"},{"time":385000,"text":"Russia, China, Pakistan, Iran."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388000,"text":"And this raises a bigger worry for me."},{"time":391000,"text":"How do we move forward in this revolution"},{"time":393000,"text":"given the state of our manufacturing"},{"time":395000,"text":"and the state of our science and"},{"time":397000,"text":"mathematics training in our schools?"},{"time":399000,"text":"Or another way of thinking about this is,"},{"time":401000,"text":"what does it mean to go to war increasingly"},{"time":403000,"text":"with soldiers whose hardware is made"},{"time":406000,"text":"in China and software is written in India?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"But just as software has gone open-source,"},{"time":414000,"text":"so has warfare."},{"time":416000,"text":"Unlike an aircraft carrier or an atomic bomb,"},{"time":419000,"text":"you don't need a massive manufacturing"},{"time":421000,"text":"system to build robotics. A lot of it is"},{"time":423000,"text":"off the shelf. A lot of it's even do-it-yourself."},{"time":425000,"text":"One of those things you just saw flashed"},{"time":427000,"text":"before you was a raven drone, the handheld"},{"time":429000,"text":"tossed one. For about a thousand dollars,"},{"time":431000,"text":"you can build one yourself, equivalent to"},{"time":433000,"text":"what the soldiers use in Iraq."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435000,"text":"That raises another wrinkle when it comes"},{"time":437000,"text":"to war and conflict. Good guys might play"},{"time":439000,"text":"around and work on these as hobby kits,"},{"time":441000,"text":"but so might bad guys."},{"time":443000,"text":"This cross between robotics and things like"},{"time":445000,"text":"terrorism is going to be fascinating"},{"time":447000,"text":"and even disturbing,"},{"time":449000,"text":"and we've already seen it start."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451000,"text":"During the war between Israel, a state,"},{"time":453000,"text":"and Hezbollah, a non-state actor,"},{"time":456000,"text":"the non-state actor flew"},{"time":458000,"text":"four different drones against Israel."},{"time":460000,"text":"There's already a jihadi website"},{"time":462000,"text":"that you can go on and remotely"},{"time":464000,"text":"detonate an IED in Iraq while sitting"},{"time":466000,"text":"at your home computer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468000,"text":"And so I think what we're going to see is"},{"time":470000,"text":"two trends take place with this."},{"time":472000,"text":"First is, you're going to reinforce the power"},{"time":474000,"text":"of individuals against governments,"},{"time":478000,"text":"but then the second is that"},{"time":480000,"text":"we are going to see an expansion"},{"time":482000,"text":"in the realm of terrorism."},{"time":484000,"text":"The future of it may be a cross between"},{"time":486000,"text":"al Qaeda 2.0 and the"},{"time":488000,"text":"next generation of the Unabomber."},{"time":490000,"text":"And another way of thinking about this"},{"time":492000,"text":"is the fact that, remember, you don't have"},{"time":494000,"text":"to convince a robot that they're gonna"},{"time":496000,"text":"receive 72 virgins after they die"},{"time":499000,"text":"to convince them to blow themselves up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502000,"text":"But the ripple effects of this are going to go"},{"time":504000,"text":"out into our politics. One of the people that"},{"time":506000,"text":"I met with was a former Assistant Secretary of"},{"time":508000,"text":"Defense for Ronald Reagan, and he put it"},{"time":510000,"text":"this way: \"I like these systems because"},{"time":512000,"text":"they save American lives, but I worry about"},{"time":514000,"text":"more marketization of wars,"},{"time":516000,"text":"more shock-and-awe talk,"},{"time":519000,"text":"to defray discussion of the costs."},{"time":521000,"text":"People are more likely to support the use"},{"time":523000,"text":"of force if they view it as costless.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":526000,"text":"Robots for me take certain trends"},{"time":528000,"text":"that are already in play in our body politic,"},{"time":531000,"text":"and maybe take them to"},{"time":533000,"text":"their logical ending point."},{"time":535000,"text":"We don't have a draft. We don't"},{"time":537000,"text":"have declarations of war anymore."},{"time":540000,"text":"We don't buy war bonds anymore."},{"time":542000,"text":"And now we have the fact that we're"},{"time":544000,"text":"converting more and more of our American"},{"time":546000,"text":"soldiers that we would send into harm's"},{"time":548000,"text":"way into machines, and so we may take"},{"time":551000,"text":"those already lowering bars to war"},{"time":554000,"text":"and drop them to the ground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557000,"text":"But the future of war is also going to be"},{"time":559000,"text":"a YouTube war."},{"time":561000,"text":"That is, our new technologies don't merely"},{"time":563000,"text":"remove humans from risk."},{"time":565000,"text":"They also record everything that they see."},{"time":568000,"text":"So they don't just delink the public:"},{"time":571000,"text":"they reshape its relationship with war."},{"time":574000,"text":"There's already several thousand"},{"time":576000,"text":"video clips of combat footage from Iraq"},{"time":578000,"text":"on YouTube right now,"},{"time":580000,"text":"most of it gathered by drones."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582000,"text":"Now, this could be a good thing."},{"time":584000,"text":"It could be building connections between"},{"time":586000,"text":"the home front and the war front"},{"time":588000,"text":"as never before."},{"time":590000,"text":"But remember, this is taking place"},{"time":592000,"text":"in our strange, weird world, and so"},{"time":595000,"text":"inevitably the ability to download these"},{"time":597000,"text":"video clips to, you know, your iPod"},{"time":599000,"text":"or your Zune gives you"},{"time":602000,"text":"the ability to turn it into entertainment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"Soldiers have a name for these clips."},{"time":608000,"text":"They call it war porn."},{"time":610000,"text":"The typical one that I was sent was"},{"time":612000,"text":"an email that had an attachment of"},{"time":614000,"text":"video of a Predator strike taking out"},{"time":616000,"text":"an enemy site. Missile hits,"},{"time":618000,"text":"bodies burst into the air with the explosion."},{"time":621000,"text":"It was set to music."},{"time":623000,"text":"It was set to the pop song"},{"time":625000,"text":"\"I Just Want To Fly\" by Sugar Ray."}]},{"cues":[{"time":628000,"text":"This ability to watch more"},{"time":631000,"text":"but experience less creates a wrinkle"},{"time":634000,"text":"in the public's relationship with war."},{"time":636000,"text":"I think about this with a sports parallel."},{"time":638000,"text":"It's like the difference between"},{"time":641000,"text":"watching an NBA game, a professional"},{"time":644000,"text":"basketball game on TV, where the athletes"},{"time":647000,"text":"are tiny figures on the screen, and"},{"time":649000,"text":"being at that basketball game in person"},{"time":652000,"text":"and realizing what someone seven feet"},{"time":654000,"text":"really does look like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656000,"text":"But we have to remember,"},{"time":658000,"text":"these are just the clips."},{"time":660000,"text":"These are just the ESPN SportsCenter"},{"time":662000,"text":"version of the game. They lose the context."},{"time":664000,"text":"They lose the strategy."},{"time":666000,"text":"They lose the humanity. War just"},{"time":668000,"text":"becomes slam dunks and smart bombs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671000,"text":"Now the irony of all this is that"},{"time":674000,"text":"while the future of war may involve"},{"time":676000,"text":"more and more machines,"},{"time":678000,"text":"it's our human psychology that's driving"},{"time":680000,"text":"all of this, it's our human failings"},{"time":682000,"text":"that are leading to these wars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684000,"text":"So one example of this that has"},{"time":686000,"text":"big resonance in the policy realm is"},{"time":688000,"text":"how this plays out on our very real"},{"time":690000,"text":"war of ideas that we're fighting"},{"time":692000,"text":"against radical groups."},{"time":694000,"text":"What is the message that we think we are"},{"time":696000,"text":"sending with these machines versus what"},{"time":698000,"text":"is being received in terms of the message."}]},{"cues":[{"time":701000,"text":"So one of the people that I met was"},{"time":703000,"text":"a senior Bush Administration official,"},{"time":705000,"text":"who had this to say about"},{"time":707000,"text":"our unmanning of war:"},{"time":709000,"text":"\"It plays to our strength. The thing that"},{"time":711000,"text":"scares people is our technology.\""},{"time":713000,"text":"But when you go out and meet with people,"},{"time":715000,"text":"for example in Lebanon, it's a very"},{"time":717000,"text":"different story. One of the people"},{"time":719000,"text":"I met with there was a news editor, and"},{"time":721000,"text":"we're talking as a drone is flying above him,"},{"time":723000,"text":"and this is what he had to say."},{"time":725002,"text":"\"This is just another sign of the coldhearted"},{"time":727000,"text":"cruel Israelis and Americans,"},{"time":730006,"text":"who are cowards because"},{"time":731998,"text":"they send out machines to fight us."},{"time":734004,"text":"They don't want to fight us like real men,"},{"time":735996,"text":"but they're afraid to fight,"},{"time":738003,"text":"so we just have to kill a few of their soldiers"},{"time":739994,"text":"to defeat them.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":742999,"text":"The future of war also is featuring"},{"time":745006,"text":"a new type of warrior,"},{"time":746999,"text":"and it's actually redefining the experience"},{"time":750005,"text":"of going to war."},{"time":752003,"text":"You can call this a cubicle warrior."},{"time":753994,"text":"This is what one Predator drone pilot"},{"time":756001,"text":"described of his experience fighting"},{"time":758008,"text":"in the Iraq War while never leaving Nevada."},{"time":760997,"text":"\"You're going to war for 12 hours,"},{"time":763002,"text":"shooting weapons at targets,"},{"time":765008,"text":"directing kills on enemy combatants,"},{"time":767999,"text":"and then you get in the car"},{"time":770005,"text":"and you drive home and within 20 minutes,"},{"time":772003,"text":"you're sitting at the dinner table"},{"time":774009,"text":"talking to your kids about their homework.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":776002,"text":"Now, the psychological balancing"},{"time":778008,"text":"of those experiences is incredibly tough,"},{"time":780001,"text":"and in fact those drone pilots have"},{"time":782993,"text":"higher rates of PTSD than many"},{"time":785001,"text":"of the units physically in Iraq."},{"time":788006,"text":"But some have worries that this"},{"time":789998,"text":"disconnection will lead to something else,"},{"time":792007,"text":"that it might make the contemplation of war"},{"time":794005,"text":"crimes a lot easier when you have"},{"time":796010,"text":"this distance. \"It's like a video game,\""},{"time":798009,"text":"is what one young pilot described to me"},{"time":800008,"text":"of taking out enemy troops from afar."},{"time":801998,"text":"As anyone who's played Grand Theft Auto"},{"time":805008,"text":"knows, we do things in the video world"},{"time":808008,"text":"that we wouldn't do face to face."}]},{"cues":[{"time":811004,"text":"So much of what you're hearing from me"},{"time":813002,"text":"is that there's another side"},{"time":814995,"text":"to technologic revolutions,"},{"time":817003,"text":"and that it's shaping our present"},{"time":818997,"text":"and maybe will shape our future of war."},{"time":821998,"text":"Moore's Law is operative,"},{"time":823999,"text":"but so's Murphy's Law."},{"time":825997,"text":"The fog of war isn't being lifted."},{"time":828002,"text":"The enemy has a vote."}]},{"cues":[{"time":830012,"text":"We're gaining incredible new capabilities,"},{"time":832001,"text":"but we're also seeing and experiencing"},{"time":834007,"text":"new human dilemmas. Now,"},{"time":836007,"text":"sometimes these are just \"oops\" moments,"},{"time":838006,"text":"which is what the head of a robotics"},{"time":839998,"text":"company described it, you just have"},{"time":842009,"text":"\"oops\" moments. Well, what are"},{"time":844009,"text":"\"oops\" moments with robots in war?"},{"time":846005,"text":"Well, sometimes they're funny. Sometimes,"},{"time":848006,"text":"they're like that scene from the"},{"time":850008,"text":"Eddie Murphy movie \"Best Defense,\""},{"time":852009,"text":"playing out in reality, where they tested out"},{"time":854010,"text":"a machine gun-armed robot, and during"},{"time":855998,"text":"the demonstration it started spinning"},{"time":857999,"text":"in a circle and pointed its machine gun"},{"time":861008,"text":"at the reviewing stand of VIPs."},{"time":864003,"text":"Fortunately the weapon wasn't loaded"},{"time":865996,"text":"and no one was hurt, but other times"},{"time":868006,"text":"\"oops\" moments are tragic,"},{"time":869998,"text":"such as last year in South Africa, where"},{"time":872000,"text":"an anti-aircraft cannon had a"},{"time":874999,"text":"\"software glitch,\" and actually did turn on"},{"time":877998,"text":"and fired, and nine soldiers were killed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":881002,"text":"We have new wrinkles in the laws of war"},{"time":883999,"text":"and accountability. What do we do"},{"time":885996,"text":"with things like unmanned slaughter?"},{"time":888006,"text":"What is unmanned slaughter?"},{"time":890004,"text":"We've already had three instances of"},{"time":892004,"text":"Predator drone strikes where we thought"},{"time":894004,"text":"we got bin Laden, and it turned out"},{"time":895998,"text":"not to be the case."},{"time":898000,"text":"And this is where we're at right now."},{"time":900008,"text":"This is not even talking about armed,"},{"time":902008,"text":"autonomous systems"},{"time":903997,"text":"with full authority to use force."},{"time":906010,"text":"And do not believe that that isn't coming."},{"time":908004,"text":"During my research I came across"},{"time":910011,"text":"four different Pentagon projects"},{"time":911996,"text":"on different aspects of that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":914008,"text":"And so you have this question:"},{"time":916010,"text":"what does this lead to issues like"},{"time":918003,"text":"war crimes? Robots are emotionless, so"},{"time":919995,"text":"they don't get upset if their buddy is killed."},{"time":923007,"text":"They don't commit crimes of rage"},{"time":925001,"text":"and revenge."},{"time":927008,"text":"But robots are emotionless."},{"time":930005,"text":"They see an 80-year-old grandmother"},{"time":932004,"text":"in a wheelchair the same way they see"},{"time":934004,"text":"a T-80 tank: they're both"},{"time":937006,"text":"just a series of zeroes and ones."},{"time":939999,"text":"And so we have this question to figure out:"},{"time":943002,"text":"How do we catch up our 20th century"},{"time":945005,"text":"laws of war, that are so old right now"},{"time":946994,"text":"that they could qualify for Medicare,"},{"time":950002,"text":"to these 21st century technologies?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":953010,"text":"And so, in conclusion, I've talked about"},{"time":955997,"text":"what seems the future of war,"},{"time":959008,"text":"but notice that I've only used"},{"time":960998,"text":"real world examples and you've only seen"},{"time":963010,"text":"real world pictures and videos."},{"time":965011,"text":"And so this sets a great challenge for"},{"time":967011,"text":"all of us that we have to worry about well"},{"time":968997,"text":"before you have to worry about your"},{"time":971006,"text":"Roomba sucking the life away from you."},{"time":973007,"text":"Are we going to let the fact that what's"},{"time":975006,"text":"unveiling itself right now in war"},{"time":978006,"text":"sounds like science fiction and therefore"},{"time":980997,"text":"keeps us in denial?"},{"time":983002,"text":"Are we going to face the reality"},{"time":985006,"text":"of 21st century war?"},{"time":986999,"text":"Is our generation going to make the same"},{"time":989000,"text":"mistake that a past generation did"},{"time":991009,"text":"with atomic weaponry, and not deal with"},{"time":993007,"text":"the issues that surround it until"},{"time":995002,"text":"Pandora's box is already opened up?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":997009,"text":"Now, I could be wrong on this, and"},{"time":999007,"text":"one Pentagon robot scientist told me"},{"time":1001011,"text":"that I was. He said, \"There's no real"},{"time":1003005,"text":"social, ethical, moral issues when it comes"},{"time":1005000,"text":"to robots."},{"time":1006998,"text":"That is,\" he added, \"unless the machine"},{"time":1008999,"text":"kills the wrong people repeatedly."},{"time":1012009,"text":"Then it's just a product recall issue.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014998,"text":"And so the ending point for this is"},{"time":1018009,"text":"that actually, we can turn to Hollywood."},{"time":1023011,"text":"A few years ago, Hollywood gathered"},{"time":1025007,"text":"all the top characters and created"},{"time":1028013,"text":"a list of the top 100 heroes and"},{"time":1030010,"text":"top 100 villains of all of Hollywood history,"},{"time":1033000,"text":"the characters that represented the best"},{"time":1035006,"text":"and worst of humanity."},{"time":1036998,"text":"Only one character made it onto both lists:"},{"time":1041013,"text":"The Terminator, a robot killing machine."},{"time":1044009,"text":"And so that points to the fact that"},{"time":1045997,"text":"our machines can be used"},{"time":1048010,"text":"for both good and evil, but for me"},{"time":1050009,"text":"it points to the fact that there's a duality"},{"time":1052005,"text":"of humans as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1055005,"text":"This week is a celebration"},{"time":1057003,"text":"of our creativity. Our creativity"},{"time":1059002,"text":"has taken our species to the stars."},{"time":1061000,"text":"Our creativity has created works of arts"},{"time":1063007,"text":"and literature to express our love."},{"time":1066003,"text":"And now, we're using our creativity"},{"time":1068001,"text":"in a certain direction, to build fantastic"},{"time":1070009,"text":"machines with incredible capabilities,"},{"time":1072996,"text":"maybe even one day"},{"time":1075005,"text":"an entirely new species."},{"time":1078002,"text":"But one of the main reasons that we're"},{"time":1080007,"text":"doing that is because of our drive"},{"time":1082005,"text":"to destroy each other, and so the question"},{"time":1085005,"text":"we all should ask:"},{"time":1086999,"text":"is it our machines, or is it us"},{"time":1088999,"text":"that's wired for war?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1091006,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}